# Apache .htaccess for API directory
# API endpoints are PUBLIC (required for desktop app) but secured with rate limiting

# Disable directory listing
Options -Indexes

# Security headers
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    Header set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
    Header set X-Frame-Options "DENY"
    Header set X-XSS-Protection "1; mode=block"
</IfModule>

# Note: API endpoints are public for desktop app functionality
# Security is handled via:
# - Rate limiting (PHP-based, 100 requests/minute per IP)
# - Session-based authentication (code + session_id)
# - Input validation (in PHP code)
# - Apache mod_ratelimit (if available)


